- Design Payment App
======================

Question - Do you want Payment Gateway or Wallet Type Application or Phonepe or Gpay  ?
Ans - Wallet Type Application


Requirement Gathering
=====================

1. Create Class Diagram and Write working code
2. Functional Req
    1. User can create acc using phone number and pass
    2. User can update profile
    3. Send Money to Other User
    4. Send Money to a bank acc
    5. Allow user to refund an transaction
    6. Allow user to make payment for transaction via card / UPI

